{"tid":766081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻省理工：未來中國人熱死的風險冠絕全球","createTime":"2018-08-03T10:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T23:17:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8e2415508fd8ddcba0185c86de7f118069329c6a","tid":766081,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:00:47.000Z","msg":"美國麻省理工學院最新研究指，全球人口最密集之一的國家中國，於本世紀末或會成為全球「最致命熱浪地區」 （deadliest heatwave zone），令中國居民熱死的風險冠絕全球。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/55599179-600x336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F55599179-600x336.jpg&h=724b62f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n帶領是次研究的塔希爾教授（Elfatih Eltahir）表示，中國目前是溫室氣體排放最多的國家。他警告：「如排放量仍然持續，未來或會影響華北平原的宜居性。」<br />\n<br />\n研究顯示，除非中國碳排放量能大幅減少，否則便會帶來潮濕熱浪，或令中國華北平原在二零七零年變得不宜居住，當中亦包括首都北京及天津等城市。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員指，一旦氣溫達「濕球溫度」（wet bulb temperature, WBT）攝氏三十五度，空氣將變得濕熱難耐，人體無法排汗降溫。研究人員又指，長期處於濕熱環境下，即使是身體健康的人士，在戶外六小時亦有可能死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/2018/08/03/%E9%BA%BB%E7%9C%81%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%86%B1%E6%AD%BB%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E5%86%A0%E7%B5%95%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E7%259C%2581%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B7%25A5%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2586%25B1%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%25B5%2595%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%2F&d=o01ryfUGnJETu8mWdWEnCf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=cceddaae\" target=\"_blank\">https://maddog.myradio.hk/2018/08/03/%E9%BA%BB%E7%9C%81%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%86%B1%E6%AD%BB%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E5%86%A0%E7%B5%95%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83/</a>"},{"pid":"56d3b84ec58a85127f1a6987a4a00fd96bc368a3