"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）至本世紀末蝗國人口只會得返4億人左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家仲有份報告話本世紀中期之後華北地區會<span style=\"color: red;\">經常</span>受到致命熱浪侵襲，簡直係北佬末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲未計其他天災人禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能共產黨崩潰之時唔知會發生咩事又一次人口大清洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚟多次咩四川地震天津核爆又<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總之呢個一百年蝗國人又要同往常嘅一百年一樣，自求多福啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909c4e6faca08f2fcb4744cf860554ea6e82dac8","tid":766081,"uid":100347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T22:21:09.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"342fca93d4c0bf82be2335fc2334ca8b19104eed","tid":766081,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5b356fbc0aef519cf7172da044f0d64c486484b","tid":766081,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:10:02.000Z","msg":"2070⋯⋯仲存在先同我講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T22:58:52.000Z","msg":"香港人會變少數"},{"pid":"f518f1d93c950b93d6015ff99107b9e533e5979c","tid":766081,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9ee2ef17cf916827eeec39c8a08db426b5ee444","tid":766081,"uid":34023,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"56d3b84ec58a85127f1a6987a4a00fd96bc368a3","tid":766081,"uid":55257,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:07:37.000Z","msg":"若然屬實，中国或成最大贏家"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:11:06.000Z","msg":"好煩又係呢句嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T22:59:19.000Z","msg":"一次就好笑"}]}